																		</fo:list-item-label>
																		<fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()">
																			<fo:block font-family="Arial" font-size="11pt" line-height="105%">U is the average U-value of all openings (window, doors, rooflights). Based on one opaque door 1.85 m² of U=1.8, any other doors fully<fo:inline xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" font-style="italic" role="html:em"> glazed</fo:inline>. For windows, doors etc a frame factor of 0.7, light transmittance 0.80 and solar energy transmittance 0.72 for U_1.7, 0.63 for U&lt;1.7 are assumed.</fo:block>
																		</fo:list-item-body>
																	</fo:list-item>
																	<fo:list-item>
																		<fo:list-item-label end-indent="label-end()">
